APT - Dependencies

Use [prgm]apt depends[/prgm] and [prgm]apt rdepends[/prgm] to explore package dependencies.

$ [prgm]apt depends[/prgm] [arg-value]package[/arg-value]               # Show what a package depends on
$ [prgm]apt rdepends[/prgm] [arg-value]package[/arg-value]              # Show what depends on a package
